Application Manager main Project 1.2-SNAPSHOT API

Packages 
Package Description
com.github.essobedo.appma.core
The package containing all the main classes of the application manger.
com.github.essobedo.appma.core.config
The package containing all the classes allowing to manipulate the Configuration.
com.github.essobedo.appma.core.io
The package containing all the classes allowing to manipulate the File objects.
com.github.essobedo.appma.core.progress
The package containing all the classes allowing to be notified of any progress of a given task.
com.github.essobedo.appma.core.util
The package containing all the utility classes used in the project.
com.github.essobedo.appma.core.zip
The package containing all the classes allowing to manipulate zip files.
com.github.essobedo.appma.exception
The package containing all the exceptions of the application manager.
com.github.essobedo.appma.i18n
The package containing everything related to the internationalization of the application.
com.github.essobedo.appma.spi
The package containing all components that are found thanks to the Service Provider Interfaces technology.
com.github.essobedo.appma.task
The package containing everything related to the tasks managed by the application manager.
